<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>١٢٤٢ - قَالَ مَعْمَرٌ ,<span class="c5"> وَقَالَ قَتَادَةُ:</span> فِي قَوْلِهِ تَعَالَى: <span class="c3">{لَا يَجْرِمَنَّكُمْ شِقَاقِي}</span> <span class="c4">[هود: ٨٩]</span> قَالَ: <span class="c2">«لَا يَحْمِلَنَّكُمْ شِقَاقٌ»</span><a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>